column2: SELECT ra_BCG, dec_BCG FROM MyDB.BCGs_SF_IN  OPEN my_cursor  WHILE(#=#) BEGIN   FETCH NEXT from my_cursor into  @ra_BCG, @dec_BCG     IF (@@fetch_status < #) break     INSERT MYDB.BCGs_SF_OUT             SELECT  @ra_BCG, @dec_BCG,                 p.ra, p.dec, p.objID,        ISNULL(s.z,#) as zs,        e.bpt            FROM   dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(@ra_BCG,@dec_BCG,#/#) n, Galaxy p   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid   JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.bestobjid=p.objid   WHERE n.objid=p.objid         END  CLOSE my_cursor DEALLOCATE my_cursor
